	abstract = {A model for the plasma atmosphere about a rotating magnetized neutron star with aligned magnetic and rotational axes is developed using a gedanken experiment in order to avoid considering at one time all of the phenomena produced by the extreme parameters associated with real pulsars. In this approach, the angular velocity of the star is
